                               FireHOL Website
                               ***************

This tree contains the sources for the FireHOL website:
  http://firehol.org

The website is built using nanoc, the install instructions for which are
here:
  http://nanoc.ws/install/

If you want to be able to run:
  nanoc view
to preview the site at:
  http://localhost:3000/
you must also install the adsf gem:
  sudo gem install adsf

For deployment under nginx, see the configuration files in the
firehol-infrastructure repository.

When adding content, pay particular attention to marking up items
with the classes used in content/semantic.css e.g.:
  <span class="filename">/var/log/messages</span>
